rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0003
rows.name:
I couldn't believe it until I saw it myself, but
it seems it was true after all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0005
rows.name: Different from the Bias... another type of alien[ST:wide ]â€•[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0006
rows.name: If we were Earth humans, what would you do?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0007
rows.name:
Annihilate.
That's our duty as Growth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0010
rows.name:
Earthlings are like
cancer cells that appeared in this universe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0011
rows.name: Our job is to eradicate it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0012
rows.name:
That's some pretty selfish logic.
Is that why you destroyed the Life Point?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0013
rows.name: You call this thing the Life Point?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0014
rows.name: So primitive. You're using pretty outdated technology.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0015
rows.name:
Well.
This thing along with you will all be eliminated.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0016
rows.name:
That's our Growth logic.
Growth's justice![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0017
rows.name: Then we'll just stick to our logic.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs04090100_MSG0018
rows.name:
Okay. Worth killing.
Much more than those guys who are just sleeping![ST:wait ]
